📂 3. Dataset Description

📄 File Used: expenses.csv
📊 Total Records: 10 rows

🏷️ Column	📖 Description
Date	The date when an expense was made
Category	Type of expense (Food, Travel, Shopping, etc.)
Amount	Expense amount in ₹ (Indian Rupees)

💡 In Milestone 2, this dataset will be expanded to 10,000–20,000 rows for forecasting tasks.

